{"tid":894463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"去subway買外賣，發動左starburst stream","createTime":"2018-11-08T12:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T12:36:48.000Z","uid":14941,"like":17,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ce344f3e601108333f4ae061f01a35dff610e5","tid":894463,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"今日去subway買外賣，有個包好似asuna 在sao買俾我食果個<br />\n<br />\n落完餐我叫佢切細份啲，佢好似聽唔明<br />\n<br />\n我：「切細份呀！切呀！」<br />\n<br />\n我拎起兩把刀，諗住要出手：「星爆....氣<br />\n<br />\n突然身後有把溫柔聲：「先生... 我估佢聽唔明中文」<br />\n<br />\n我點點頭。答：「了解。條人龍好長，幫我撐十秒！」<br />\n<br />\n我：「starburst.....stream!!!!!」<br />\n<br />\n熟蛋隨即變成碎蛋。<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8b64930d74bb1aa1f5297b68ee7f3c268d7bbd08","tid":894463,"uid":187227,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"feel到你盡力了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64be52db091efd42ab753babfc2919a4668bd54","tid":894463,"uid":94454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcb9c756895dfd113f457ee26b24776848047a6","tid":894463,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e546092eb38b343c48bc33fa26ff0dfeb4924a1","tid":894463,"uid":167721,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:15:27.000Z","msg":"今次好尷尬"},{"pid":"9f2c73125fb62b9d88888a745f0b4fc953440c82","tid":894463,"uid":146340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:16:25.000Z","msg":"回晒塘 無計 要負評"},{"pid":"53d584d727d95dd4eb742e1d06d08103612b4407","tid":894463,"uid":22079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7d6e53334670048edcf243f92549ee6b7ecec39c","tid":894463,"uid":31429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc